flowchart LR
    LOAD[Traffic Load]

    LOAD --> P50[p50 latency]
    LOAD --> P99[p99 latency]
    LOAD --> ERR[error rate %]

    P50 & P99 & ERR --> BUDGET[latency budget check]
    BUDGET -->|within budget| OK[healthy]
    BUDGET -->|budget exhausted| THROTTLE[throttle / shed load]
    THROTTLE --> SCALE[trigger autoscale]
    SCALE --> CAP[capacity added]
    CAP --> RECOVER[latency recovers]
